de.lessvoid.niftyinternal.common

Class Box

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.lessvoid.niftyinternal.common.Box

  • public class Box
extends Object
    The Box class represent a rectangular area on the screen. It has a position (x,y) as well as height and weight attributes. The Box represent an already resolved position in pixels.
    Author:
    void
